{"word":"G5576 - ψευδομαρτυρέω - pseudomartyréō - psyoo-dom-ar-too-reh'-o - Be a false witness","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ψευδομαρτυρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pseudomartyréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">psyoo-dom-ar-too-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be a false witness</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பொய்சாட்சி சொல்"},{"paragraph":"to utter falsehoods in giving testimony, to testify falsely, to bear false witness"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5575 - ψευδομάρτυρ - pseudomártyr - psyoo-dom-ar'-toor/5575\">G5575</a>; to <i>be an untrue testifier</i>, that is, offer <i>falsehood in evidence:</i> - be a false witness.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1263/1263\">G1263</a>, <a href=\"#/G1957/1957\">G1957</a>, <a href=\"#/G2649/2649\">G2649</a>, <a href=\"#/G3140/3140\">G3140</a>, <a href=\"#/G3141/3141\">G3141</a>, <a href=\"#/G3142/3142\">G3142</a>, <a href=\"#/G3143/3143\">G3143</a>, <a href=\"#/G3144/3144\">G3144</a>, <a href=\"#/G4303/4303\">G4303</a>, <a href=\"#/G4828/4828\">G4828</a>, <a href=\"#/G4901/4901\">G4901</a>, <a href=\"#/G5571/5571\">G5571</a>, <a href=\"#/G5572/5572\">G5572</a>, <a href=\"#/G5573/5573\">G5573</a>, <a href=\"#/G5574/5574\">G5574</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575/5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576/5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577/5577\">G5577</a>, <a href=\"#/G5578/5578\">G5578</a>, <a href=\"#/G5579/5579\">G5579</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580/5580\">G5580</a>, <a href=\"#/G5581/5581\">G558